data.description: 3 br 1.5 bath brick ranch home w/basement on approx .673 acre lot. Home has a covered front porch, rear concrete deck, covered rear patio & attached single carport. The playset & 2 outbuildings remain. Living Room gets plenty of natural light. Family Room has a fireplace. Dining Room is spacious, has a breakfast bar & French doors to the rear deck. Kitchen has stainless appliances & plenty of cabinets. The refrigerator remains. Primary Bedroom has an attached half bath. The laundry area is in the unfinished basement. The rear deck is a great place for entertaining or just relaxing. Home is being sold cash or conventional only.
